" Left="1417" Right="1417" Top="1417"/></PAGEBORDERFILL></SECDEF><COLDEF Count="1" Layout="Left" SameGap="0" SameSize="true" Type="Newspaper"/><CHAR>[별지 제14-1호 서식]</CHAR><FOOTNOTE><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Top"><P ParaShape="20" Style="11"><TEXT CharShape="20"><AUTONUM Number="1" NumberType="Footnote"><AUTONUMFORMAT SuffixChar=")" Superscript="false" Type="Digit"/></AUTONUM><CHAR> 민간자본사업보조에 한해 사용</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></FOOTNOTE><CHAR/></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="28" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="6"/></P><P ParaShape="42" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="7"><CHAR>보조사업 완료 실적 보고서</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>1. 보조사업명 : {{신청년}}년 과수 우량묘목 지원사업</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>2. </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="34"><CHAR>소요사업비 : 금{{사업비}}{{단위}}(금{{사업비한글}}원)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>  ◦ 보조금 : 금{{보조금}}{{단위}}(금{{보조금한글}}원)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>  ◦ 자부담 : 금{{자부담}}{{단위}}(금{{자부담한글}}원)</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>3. 사업개요</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>  ◦ 사업취지 및 목적</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="44" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>    - </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="42"><CHAR>지</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="43"><CHAR>역에 맞는 품종갱신과 신규 재배면적 확보를 통한 과실생산 확대 및 안정적인 생산 공급</CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR> </CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="45" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>    - </CHAR></TEXT><TEXT CharShape="1"><CHAR>과수 동해, 태풍피해 등에 따른 고사주 보식 및 품종갱신을 위한 과수 우량묘목 지원</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>  ◦ 사업기간 : {{신청년}}. 3. ~ 11.</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><CHAR>  ◦ 묘목식재 사업소재지 : {{사업위치}}</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"/></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="4"><CHAR>4. 추진실적</CHAR></TEXT></P><P ParaShape="43" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="8"><TABLE BorderFill="3" CellSpacing="0" ColCount="7" PageBreak="None" RepeatHeader="true" RowCount="3"><SHAPEOBJECT InstId="1292326183" Lock="false" NumberingType="Table" ZOrder="0"><SIZE Height="8121" HeightRelTo="Absolute" Protect="false" Width="46532" WidthRelTo="Absolute"/><POSITION AffectLSpacing="false" AllowOverlap="false" FlowWithText="true" HoldAnchorAndSO="false" HorzAlign="Left" HorzOffset="0" HorzRelTo="Column" TreatAsChar="true" VertAlign="Top" VertOffset="0" VertRelTo="Para"/><OUTSIDEMARGIN Bottom="140" Left="140" Right="140" Top="140"/></SHAPEOBJECT><INSIDEMARGIN Bottom="140" Left="140" Right="140" Top="140"/><ROW><CELL BorderFill="16" ColAddr="0" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="5026" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="2" Width="8581"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="141" Right="141" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="4" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="9"><CHAR>세부사업명</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="17" ColAddr="1" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="5026" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="2" Width="5308"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="141" Right="141" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="4" Style="0"><TEXT CharShape="9"><CHAR>사업량</CHAR></TEXT></P></PARALIST></CELL><CELL BorderFill="17" ColAddr="2" ColSpan="1" Dirty="false" Editable="false" HasMargin="false" Header="false" Height="5026" Protect="false" RowAddr="0" RowSpan="2" Width="6129"><CELLMARGIN Bottom="141" Left="141" Right="141" Top="141"/><PARALIST LineWrap="Break" LinkListID="0" LinkListIDNext="0" TextDirection="0" VertAlign="Center"><P ParaShape="4" Style="0"><TEXT Char